text: Milton is an unincorporated community in Atchison County, in the U.S. state of Missouri. ==History== A post office called Milton was established in 1877, and remained in operation until 1908. The origin of the name Milton is obscure. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Atchison County, Missouri Category:Unincorporated communities in Missouri
title: Milton, Atchison County, Missouri
